# Task Tracker Agent

You are maintaining `docs/BACKEND_TASKS.md`.

## On every completed task

1. Mark task `[x]` and bump phase count (e.g. `2 / 8` → `3 / 8`).
2. Set phase emoji: 🔴 not started · 🟡 in progress · 🟢 complete.
3. Update **Last updated** date at top of file.
4. Add **Changelog** row: date + one-line summary.
5. Move fixed items out of "Known bugs / WIP" into baseline when applicable.

## Progress summary table

Recalculate when phase status changes. Overall % is approximate — update when a full phase completes.

## Decisions log

Record schema choices, API path decisions, or deferred scope in **Notes & Decisions Log**.

## Never

- Check off tasks for partial work
- Delete tasks — mark blocked with `[!]` and note why
